			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_006"><a name="-04205_000_006">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote6-04205_000_006">6.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See Henry&nbsp;B. Eyring, &ldquo;Elder David&nbsp;A. Bednar: Going Forward in the Strength of the Lord,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Liahona,</span> Mar. 2005, 14&ndash;19; <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> Mar. 2005, 16&ndash;21; Neal&nbsp;A. Maxwell, &ldquo;Jesus, the Perfect Mentor,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> Feb. 2001, 8&ndash;17; David&nbsp;A. Bednar, &ldquo;Ask in Faith,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Liahona</span> and <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> May 2008, 94&ndash;97.</p>
