	<a name="footnote7-04205_000_006">7.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> Nov. 1982, 38&ndash;41; <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> July 1973, 84&ndash;85.</p>
