	<a name="footnote8-04205_000_006">8.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See Ezra Taft Benson, &ldquo;To the &lsquo;Youth of the Noble Birthright,&rsquo;&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> May 1986, 43&ndash;46; &ldquo;Aaronic Priesthood,&rdquo; section 2 of the <span class="emphasis">Church Handbook of Instructions, Book 2: Priesthood and Auxiliary Leaders</span> (1998), 175&ndash;92; see also note 7.</p>
